":174197,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T17:04:07.000Z","msg":"攰就抖下先 仲有其他人幫手頂住"},{"pid":"582b51b15eeffd7387af3e8f5390b291a2e95360","tid":1437880,"uid":236011,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a4d949956ad6445d3450cfc13d1fd61bb2ce15fd","tid":1437880,"uid":174197,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T17:04:07.000Z","msg":"攰就抖下先 仲有其他人幫手頂住"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T17:06:20.000Z","msg":"知道啦 多謝你地<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f46d41435fd2967180b2e7e3263e100246947e7b","tid":1437880,"uid":271162,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T17:17:59.000Z","msg":"辛苦就上嚟呻，呢度實有唔少同路人。但反面就唔讚成，兄弟爬山，唔同人唔同處境，唔係話你出到去先有貢獻。<br />\n例如你慳咗搬出去住舊錢，拎一千幾百，幫助吓貧苦兒童，捐助吓612，而且記住，無論今次運動因咩原因靜咗落嚟都好，各手足前面仲有一條好長嘅路要一齊行。<br />\n我自己本身亦有所限制唔可以成日夢遊，但我俾自己目標，就係要幫返為咗我哋而被補嘅手足。"},{"pid":"e352c7e7ed602f6e557a30a6c302cfd38be8e4a6","tid":1437880,"uid":263279,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T17:19:20.000Z","msg":"唔好覺得自己幫唔到手, 就算唔落場都可以做鍵盤戰士<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n未夠能力獨立就死忍多陣<br />\n記住要係自己能力範圍內幫手, 顧好自己先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">最後, 祝你兩老落街食煙比狗打<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span>"},{"pid":"717ce4ea88fd91a0541d1e65ea0ac4a585bef32c","tid":1437880,"uid":236011,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e352c7e7ed602f6e557a30a6c302cfd38be8e4a6","tid":1437880,"uid":263279,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T17:19:20.000Z","msg":"唔好覺得自己幫唔到手, 就算唔落場都可以做鍵盤戰士<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n未夠能力獨立就死忍多陣<br />\n記住要係自己能力範圍內幫手, 顧好自己先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">最後, 祝你兩老落街食煙比狗打<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\"